Title: COMBINING TWO CLASSICAL APPROACHES FOR STATISTICAL SELECTION  
Author: J.H.M. Verheijen F.P.A.Coolen and P. van der Laan 
Keyword: Key Words: indifference zone selection; normal populations; preference threshold; probability of correct selection; subset selection  
Address: P.O. Box  5600 MB Eindhoven Durham, DH1 3LE The Netherlands England  
Note: Correspondence address:  
Affiliation: Eindhoven University of Technology  Eindhoven University of Technology zUniversity of Durham Dep. of Mathematics and Computing Science Dep. of Mathematical Sciences  Science Laboratories  
Pubnum: Memorandum COSOR  
